column5: The best song IMO  <object style="height: 390px; width: 640px"><param name="movie" value="http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=mwircEDCss8?version=3"><param'>http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=mwircEDCss8?version=3"><param name="allowFullScreen" value="true"><param name="allowScriptAccess" value="always"><embed src="http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=mwircEDCss8?version=3" type="application/x-shockwave-flash" allowfullscreen="true" allowScriptAccess="always" width="640" height="390"></object>
B put the lid back on the glue bottle  ....this is the best ND song

That's just too funny Brian.  For the last week or more I've been sending my daughter at University a "song for the day," just to keep in touch with her. Yesterday it was a Neil Diamond tune, not because I'm a huge fan but because it reminds me of my father who liked Neil but unfortunately died a young man.  I sent her this....  http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=s6FfjlxZLTk&feature=related  Rose also happens to be her mother's name.
Happy 70th to one of the Greats!   My favourite!
